
flowchart TB

subgraph Users
U1[Employee User]
U2[IT Administrator]
end

subgraph User_Devices
D1[Corporate Laptop]
D2[Mobile Device]
D3[Web Browser]
end

subgraph Identity_Provider
AAD[Azure Entra ID / Azure AD]
Directory[Azure AD Directory]
MFA[Multi-Factor Authentication]
CA[Conditional Access Policies]
end

subgraph Identity_Protocols
SAML[SAML 2.0 Federation]
OIDC[OpenID Connect]
OAuth[OAuth 2.0 Authorization]
end

subgraph Enterprise_Applications
App1[Salesforce]
App2[ServiceNow]
App3[Microsoft 365]
App4[Custom Internal Web App]
end

subgraph Identity_Provisioning
HR[HR System]
SCIM[SCIM Provisioning Service]
end

U1 --> D1
U1 --> D2
U2 --> D3

D1 --> AAD
D2 --> AAD
D3 --> AAD

AAD --> Directory
AAD --> MFA
AAD --> CA

AAD --> SAML
AAD --> OIDC
AAD --> OAuth

SAML --> App1
SAML --> App2

OIDC --> App3
OAuth --> App4

HR --> SCIM
SCIM --> AAD
